title: Holiday Lounge - The Christmas Remixes
description:
This is a great album of Christmas remixes.  The remixes are done really well, and aren't like those annoying Christmas songs that are done over by famous artists and sound horrible.  Nice to play as background music at a party, opening presents, etc.

MP3s are encoded at 256kbps.

Enjoy, and seed! :)


Track listing:


1. Happy Holiday (Beef Wellington Remix) - Bing Crosby
2. Frosty The Snowman (Rondo Brothers Remix) - Patti Page
3. Jingle Bells (Dan The Automator Remix) - Dean Martin
4. Baby, It's Cold Outside (Mulato Beat Remix) - Louis Armstrong & Velma Middleton
5. I'll Be Home For Christmas (Ohmega Watts Remix) - Charles Brown
6. White Christmas (Kaskade Remix) - Bing Crosby
7. Winter Wonderland (Future Loop Foundation Remix) - Vic Damone
8. The Christmas Song (Jay Rodriguez & Rev Scott Remix) - Mel Torme
9. Jingle Bell Rock (Q-Burns Abstract Message Remix) - Bobby Helms
10. Dance Of The Sugar Plum Fairy (Red Baron Remix) - Berlin Symphony Orchestra
11. Christmas Bells (Northern Elektrix Remix) - Patti Page
12. Rudolph, The Red-Nosed Reindeer (John Beltran Remix) - Bing Crosby & Ella Fitzgerald
13. Jingle Bells (Rise Ashen's Reindeer Dub) - Duke Ellington
14. The Christmas Song (Patrick Krouchian Remix)
